With the holidays fast approaching, some students may be wondering what teachers like to receive as gifts. Palo Alto High School teachers responded to The Paly Voice’s question: What kind of gifts have you received that you find to be most memorable or thoughtful?

<em>Photos by Jeanette Wong.</em>
